<h3>To reset your password click the link below:</h3>

<h5> Rails Link: <%= link_to "Change Password", edit_password_reset_path(@user.reset_digest) %> </h5>
<h5> HTML Link: <a href="localhost:3000/password_resets/<%= @user.reset_digest %>/edit" target="_blank">Reset Password</a> </h5>
<h5> Hardcoded link: http://www.herokuapp.com/password_resets/<%=@user.reset_digest%>/edit </h5>

<p>
  This link will expire in two hours.
</p>
<p>
  If you did not request your password to be reset, please ignore this email and
  your password will stay as it is.
</p>
